text: James Townsend (20 June 1937 – 7 January 2021) was an Irish Labour Party politician. In 1991, he was elected to Carlow County Council. He was a member of the Seanad Éireann from 1993 to 1997. Townsend died on 7 January 2021, aged 83. ==References== Category:1937 births Category:2021 deaths Category:Irish politicians
